{"tid":1091423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田空置舖遭噴刑毀字句 業主友上門收舖揭發","createTime":"2019-04-04T06:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T06:26:45.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a10f4645066448dbeff43eef94758b3ec5af9593","tid":1091423,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJEvcO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJEvcO1.png&h=7197cbae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鐵閘噴上「隱瞞漏水」字句，警員到場調查。張培生攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4EZQAH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4EZQAH.png&h=9f7e96c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fh65L82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffh65L82.png&h=7c62d434&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03KK1Ho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03KK1Ho.png&h=666e0ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田大涌橋路河畔花園一個空置地舖，早上10時34分，業主託女親友為他收回舖位，女親友登門查看，發現店舖的大門鐵閘及店內牆身，分別遭人用黑色及紅色的漆油噴上控訴的字句，包括鐵閘噴上「隱瞞漏水」，店內牆身則噴上「無良業主」等，女親友報警求助，警員到場列刑毀事件處理，並聯絡前租客了解事件。據附近舖頭職員表示，空置店舖前身為一間足浴店。　"},{"pid":"c7b31635fc9eb88d1cf0996b873251814d0a152b","tid":1091423,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"寫錯字 + 寫殘廢字"}]}